Lines in the xy-plane

Show that A(x - x0) + B(y - y0) = 0 is an equation
for the line in the xy-plane through the point (x0, y0)
normal to the vector N = Ai + Bj


xoozi, 这个的证明, 比较有意思, 我一下没想到

设P(x, y)是该直线上的点
则向量v = (x - x0)i + (y - y0)j 平行于该直线


而v · N = A(x - x0) + B(x - y0) = 0

故v与N正交,
故该直线与N正交
